<L>__{exterior downtown monrovia street. night.}
<A>__{yuri walks down a poorly lit sidestreet. he feels something in his back stops abruptly. his hand reflexively goes to his holster. empty. he turns. the young liberian man is holding him up with his own gun.}
<C>__{yuri}
